title: Over 40,000 Oil Paintings and Drawings [Organized]
description:
First off I have to give credit to DesiderataHun for uploading the original torrent. I thought it was so badly organized that I would go ahead and spend some time to fix it and reupload it. 

I went through EVERY artist and EVERY folder. I deleted everything that was corrupt. I reorganized every artist by their correct name. I tried to get rid of every duplicate file. I would say I got rid of 99% of them. I kept a few because of the difference in resolution, color, etc...

Enjoy, this is my first torrent so I'm sorry if there are any mistakes. If there is anything wrong, please write it in the comments below.
